Irwin Simon
 


 A word from Irwin Simon, CEO of The Hain Celestial Group










 




From the beginning, we have advocated bringing healthier products to market and making them available in all types of stores and communities. We have often led the way with unpopular positions that later proved to be right, distinguishing our products from those of others with our commitment to wholesome eating. 
For example, we have never had transfats, artificial flavors or colors and dyes, or high-fructose corn syrup in our natural foods and beverages. We are also committed to helping to fight record high levels of obesity – tone of the most critical health concerns of our time.
Hain Celestial also takes steps every year to reduce our environmental footprint while strengthening our communities as we drive profitable business growth. To us, that is the true measure of success.
Irwin Simon












